{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_06_01_short",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 掴めない感覚 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタイン前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day before Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ここの振付は、当日のステージ規模を考えると……\nカメラワークも確認したいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography here‚ considering the stage size on the day…\nI also want to check the camera work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ good job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ Hello.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれはさっき駅まで見送りに行ったよ。優はもうすぐ\nソロの仕事が終わるから、この後迎えに行くつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire just went to see off someone at the station earlier.\nI'm going to pick Yu up after her solo job is finished soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you as always.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタイン当日のスペシャルライブの準備はどうだ？\n最近練習の様子を見れてなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are the preparations for the Valentine's Day special live going?\nI haven't been able to see the practice lately‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "順調ですよ。今はステージに合わせた細かい調整を\n考えていたところです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's going smoothly. Right now‚\nI'm thinking about fine-tuning to match the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4333341598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "なので、ステージングの方は大丈夫なんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the staging should be fine‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　他に悩みがあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Is there something else bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……その、バレンタインの新曲とCM撮影で\n行き詰まっていることがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I've been stuck with the new Valentine's Day song\nand the CM shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影は、キスシーンのことで悩んでたよな\nでも、曲の方でも悩みがあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were worried about the kissing scene in the shoot‚ right?\nBut‚ do you also have concerns about the new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "はい。どちらも気持ちが……\n自分の想いが乗り切らない感覚があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I have mixed feelings about both…\nI have this feeling that my own emotions aren't coming through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333341598,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}